---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Build AI-Powered PBL With Us | PBL Future Labs">
    <!-- Page Header -->
    <section class="scroll-reveal" style="padding: 4rem 0 3rem;">
        <h1 class="mb-4">Build it with us.</h1>
        <p style="color: #6B6560; font-size: 1.1rem; max-width: 520px;">Work directly with Thom Markham, Ph.D. and Phil Alcock. From a single conversation to a full school transformation — we'll help you implement Project-Based AI Experiences.</p>
    </section>

    <div class="section-divider"></div>

    <!-- What You Walk Away With — LEAD WITH THIS -->
    <section class="scroll-reveal" style="padding: 2rem 0 3rem;">
        <h2 class="mb-10">What you walk away with.</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div>
                <h3 class="mb-2" style="font-size: 1rem;">A clear implementation plan</h3>
                <p style="color: #6B6560; font-size: 0.9rem;">Step-by-step roadmap tailored to your school's context, standards, and student needs.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3 class="mb-2" style="font-size: 1rem;">Ready-to-use AI prompts and workflows</h3>
                <p style="color: #6B6560; font-size: 0.9rem;">Tested prompts for project design, differentiation, and assessment — ready for your next unit.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3 class="mb-2" style="font-size: 1rem;">PBL project design systems</h3>
                <p style="color: #6B6560; font-size: 0.9rem;">Thom Markham's proven project design templates — the same ones used in our courses, adapted for your school.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3 class="mb-2" style="font-size: 1rem;">Ongoing confidence</h3>
                <p style="color: #6B6560; font-size: 0.9rem;">The knowledge and support to keep building long after the session ends.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="section-divider"></div>

    <!-- Coaching Tiers -->
    <section class="scroll-reveal" style="padding: 2rem 0 3rem;">
        <h2 class="mb-4">Choose how to work with us.</h2>
        <p class="mb-10" style="color: #6B6560; max-width: 480px;">Whether you're exploring the idea or ready to transform your school, there's a way in.</p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <!-- Tier 1: First Conversation -->
            <div class="coaching-tier-card">
                <p style="color: #0D9488; font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.8rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Getting started</p>
                <h3 style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">First Conversation</h3>
                <p style="color: #6B6560; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">A focused 30-minute call to talk through your goals, your context, and where AI-powered PBL fits.</p>
                <p style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 500; color: #1A1A1A; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Free</p>
                <p style="color: #6B6560; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">30 minutes, virtual</p>
                <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6" style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #6B6560;">
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: #0D9488;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        Needs assessment
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: #0D9488;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        Quick-win recommendations
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: #0D9488;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        No obligation
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <a href="mailto:hello@pblfuturelabs.com?subject=First Conversation Request" class="btn-primary-teal w-full text-center" style="display: block;">Book a call</a>
            </div>

            <!-- Tier 2: Design Sprint -->
            <div class="coaching-tier-card coaching-tier-featured">
                <p style="color: #0D9488; font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.8rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Most popular</p>
                <h3 style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Design Sprint</h3>
                <p style="color: #6B6560; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">A 60-minute hands-on session where we solve a specific challenge or co-design your AI-powered PBL implementation plan.</p>
                <p style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 500; color: #1A1A1A; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">$249</p>
                <p style="color: #6B6560; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">60 minutes, virtual or in-person</p>
                <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6" style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #6B6560;">
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: #0D9488;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        Focused problem-solving
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: #0D9488;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        Custom action plan
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: #0D9488;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        Follow-up email summary
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: #0D9488;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        Resource recommendations
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <a href="mailto:hello@pblfuturelabs.com?subject=Design Sprint Request" class="btn-primary-teal w-full text-center" style="display: block;">Book a session</a>
            </div>

            <!-- Tier 3: School Transformation -->
            <div class="coaching-tier-card">
                <p style="color: #0D9488; font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.8rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">For schools & districts</p>
                <h3 style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">School Transformation Program</h3>
                <p style="color: #6B6560; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">A sustained partnership for schools and districts. We embed with your team — coaching, workshops, curriculum design, and leadership support.</p>
                <p style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 500; color: #1A1A1A; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Custom</p>
                <p style="color: #6B6560; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Monthly, virtual + in-person</p>
                <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6" style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #6B6560;">
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: #0D9488;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        School-wide PBL rollout
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: #0D9488;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        Teacher workshops
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: #0D9488;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        Leadership coaching
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: #0D9488;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        Custom curriculum design
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <a href="mailto:hello@pblfuturelabs.com?subject=School Transformation Inquiry" class="btn-primary-teal w-full text-center" style="display: block;">Get in touch</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="section-divider"></div>

    <!-- Session Types -->
    <section class="scroll-reveal" style="padding: 2rem 0 3rem;">
        <h2 class="mb-10">Session types.</h2>
        <div class="space-y-10">
            <div>
                <h3 class="mb-2">1:1 Coaching</h3>
                <p style="color: #6B6560;">Personalized sessions for individual educators. You'll walk away with a concrete implementation plan and specific AI workflows for your next project.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="divider-line"></div>
            <div>
                <h3 class="mb-2">Small Group</h3>
                <p style="color: #6B6560;">Ideal for department teams or grade-level groups (3-8 educators). Collaborative planning with hands-on practice designing AI-enhanced projects together.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="divider-line"></div>
            <div>
                <h3 class="mb-2">School Team</h3>
                <p style="color: #6B6560;">Full staff workshops and multi-session implementation support. Includes leadership coaching, teacher training, and curriculum design.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="section-divider"></div>

    <!-- Your Coaches -->
    <section class="scroll-reveal" style="padding: 2rem 0 3rem;">
        <h2 class="mb-10">Who you'll work with.</h2>
        <div class="space-y-12">
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 items-start">
                <div class="w-32 h-32 flex-shrink-0 overflow-hidden img-skeleton" style="border-radius: 8px;">
                    <img
                        src="/images/thom.webp"
                        alt="Thom Markham, Ph.D."
                        width="128"
                        height="128"
                        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                        loading="lazy"
                        decoding="async"
                        onload="this.parentElement.classList.add('loaded')"
                    />
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="mb-1">Thom Markham, Ph.D.</h3>
                    <p class="mb-3" style="color: #0D9488; font-size: 0.85rem;">Author & PBL Expert</p>
                    <p style="color: #6B6560;">Author of three bestselling PBL books, including <em>Project-Based Learning Handbook</em>. Ph.D. in Psychology. Thom has trained thousands of educators across 15+ years and brings deep expertise in learning science, project design, and assessment to every session.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="divider-line"></div>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 items-start">
                <div class="w-32 h-32 flex-shrink-0" style="border-radius: 8px; background-color: #EDE8E3; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                    <span style="font-size: 2.5rem; color: #6B6560;">PA</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="mb-1">Phil Alcock</h3>
                    <p class="mb-3" style="color: #0D9488; font-size: 0.85rem;">Co-Founder, PBL Future Labs</p>
                    <p style="color: #6B6560;">ISTE speaker. Harvard guest lecturer. Built a community of 10,000+ educators on LinkedIn. Phil designs the AI workflows, project systems, and classroom strategies used across all PBL Future Labs programs. He's the one who figured out how to make AI work inside real PBL units — and he'll show you how.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="section-divider"></div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="scroll-reveal text-center" style="padding: 2rem 0 4rem;">
        <h2 class="mb-4">Ready to start?</h2>
        <p class="mb-8" style="color: #6B6560; max-width: 420px; margin: 0 auto;">Your first conversation is free. Tell us about your school and we'll recommend the best path forward.</p>
        <a href="mailto:hello@pblfuturelabs.com?subject=Coaching Inquiry" class="btn-primary-teal">Book a free call &rarr;</a>
    </section>
</Layout>
